{"tid":294044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電話地址被公開朱智賢考慮報警","createTime":"2017-06-22T15:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T01:56:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0234cb9253d6cfcc75d7cc325d05eb1368fbdb","tid":294044,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh_Hant_hk/News/TheSun/0622-00282-012b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh_Hant_hk%2FNews%2FTheSun%2F0622-00282-012b1.jpg&h=f40fb559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫小花朱智賢（Ashley）近日在網上投訴一間寵物美容服務公司不守承諾，服務態度欠佳，該名寵物美容師其後發長文反擊，先為遲到致歉，但又表達不滿，指「做零售業做錯少少就係咁畀人公審」，更公開與Ashley的WhatsApp對話截圖，洩露了其電話及地址。<br />\n<br />\nAshley昨晚受訪時表示，收到一個陌生人通知，才知道私隱被公開，她找該美容師對質，對方只表示一時按錯，沒有道歉！Ashley說：「我問咗意見，諗住報警或者搵私隱專員公署，因為已經有陌生人拎咗我電話。」"},{"pid":"7d2a3ceb2f656c2e0b38c05bbb95b5e65e19d4a1","tid":294044,"uid":34926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"照妖鏡.."},{"pid":"da3ab323112aeeabc2f8fea7a228d8e12526bf06","tid":294044,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d7f96de9c2c6dbcd00b1c177c58cbaca1386f02","tid":294044,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下有得咁告?</blockquote><br />\n應該有掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9181376bf29f040517ef73ca35ec13f873205558","tid":294044,"uid":5015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T00:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照妖鏡..</blockquote><br />\n都好撚正咼"},{"pid":"c676c239513971b156680cd9ae07048992968035","tid":294044,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下有得咁告?</blockquote><br />\n應該有掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去幫趁